As a data scientist focused on risk and control assurance, I am always looking for new challenges and ways to expand my skill set. I believe a copilot license would not only provide a unique perspective on decision-making and precision but also offer me a practical, real-world application of data analytics and risk management in the aviation industry. Additionally, I am eager to combine my technical background with the experience of navigating complex environments, and I see this license as an opportunity for personal growth and an extension of my analytical skills in high-stakes settings.